-- Gunman Fires From Roof in Finland, Kills Two, Injures Seven: YLE
-- B y   K a t i   P o h j a n p a l o
-- 2012-05-26T08:47:17Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-05-26/gunman-fires-from-roof-in-finland-kills-two-injures-seven-yle.html
A gunman opened fire from the roof of
a building early this morning in Hyvinkaeae, southern  Finland ,
killing two people, state-owned broadcaster  YLE reported  on its
website.  An 18-year-old man and 18-year-old woman were killed and
seven people were injured, the Helsinki-based broadcaster said.
One of the injured is a 23-year-old female police officer. An
18-year-old man suspected to be the killer was apprehended by
the police before 8 a.m. local time, YLE said.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Kati Pohjanpalo at 
 kpohjanpalo@bloomberg.net  